#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enhancing the OpenAPI Schema with Filters"
msgstr "使用过滤器增强 OpenAPI 模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can change the Generated OpenAPI Schema using one or more filter. Filters can run during build time, or at runtime."
msgstr "您可以使用一个或多个过滤器来修改生成的 OpenAPI 架构。过滤器可以在构建时或运行时执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Annotate the class with `@OpenApiFilter` and use the `stages` field with one or more of `BUILD`, `RUNTIME_STARTUP`, or `RUNTIME_PER_REQUEST`. This filter runs once during build, and once every time the OpenAPI document is requested."
msgstr "在类上添加 `@OpenApiFilter` 注解，并在 `stages` 字段中指定一个或多个以下选项： `BUILD` 、 `RUNTIME_STARTUP` 或 `RUNTIME_PER_REQUEST` 。该过滤器在构建期间运行一次，并在每次请求 OpenAPI 文档时运行一次。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Implement OASFilter and override any of its methods"
msgstr "实现 OASFilter 接口并重写其任意方法"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Filters which run during the build of the application - i.e. `BUILD` Stage filters (See also <<Advanced interactions of RunStages>>) - the Jandex index can be passed in the constructor. During application runtime, the Jandex index will *not* be null. However it will be empty, i.e it won't contain info about any classes or annotations."
msgstr "在应用程序构建过程中运行的过滤器——即 `BUILD` 阶段过滤器（另请参阅 <<Advanced interactions of RunStages>> ）——可以在构造函数中传入 Jandex 索引。 在应用程序运行期间，Jandex 索引 *不会* 为 null。但它将是空的，即不包含任何类或注解的信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Get a hold of the generated `OpenAPI` Schema, and enhance as required"
msgstr "获取生成的 `OpenAPI` 架构，并根据需要进行完善"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/openapi-swaggerui.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Remember that setting fields on the schema will override what has been generated, you might want to get and add to (so modify). Also know that the generated values might be null, so you will have to check for that."
msgstr "请注意，在模式中设置字段会覆盖生成的内容，您可能需要先获取这些字段，然后进行追加（即修改）。此外，请注意生成的值可能是空值，因此您需要对此进行检查。"

